    TERMINAL 1 
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
source ~/turtlebot_ws/install/setup.bash
export TURTLEBOT3_MODEL=burger
ros2 launch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_world.launch.py

    TERMINAL 2
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
source ~/turtlebot_ws/install/setup.bash
export TURTLEBOT3_MODEL=burger
ros2 launch turtlebot3_navigation2 navigation2.launch.py use_sim_time:=True map:=/home/vboxuser/map.yaml

    FOR NAVIGATION IN RVIZ
Terminal 3 – Send goals

RViz will open automatically

Use 2D Pose Estimate (green arrow) → set robot’s initial position on the map

Use 2D Nav Goal (green flag) → click anywhere on the map → bot drives there autonomously
